ss=\"external text\" href=\"http://rcnpublishing.com/doi/pdfplus/10.7748/ns2010.01.24.20.35.c7453\">\"Role of the nurse-to-nurse handover in patient care\"</a>. <i>Nursing Standard</i>. <b>24</b> (20): 35\u201339. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.7748/ns2010.01.24.20.35.c7453\">10.7748/ns2010.01.24.20.35.c7453</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">10 October</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Nursing+Standard&amp;rft.atitle=Role+of+the+nurse-to-nurse+handover+in+patient+care.&amp;rft.volume=24&amp;rft.issue=20&amp;rft.pages=35-39&amp;rft.date=2010&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.7748%2Fns2010.01.24.20.35.c7453&amp;rft.aulast=Scovell&amp;rft.aufirst=S&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Frcnpublishing.com%2Fdoi%2Fpdfplus%2F10.7748%2Fns2010.01.24.20.35.c7453&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AChange-of-shift+report\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Institute of Medicine. (2001). Crossing the quality chasm: A new health system for the 21st century. Washington, DC: National Academies Press.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-:1-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-:1_5-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-:1_5-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Agency for Healthcare Research and Quality. (2013). Strategy 3: Nurse bedside shift report (Implementation handbook). Retrieved from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.ahrq.gov/professionals/systems/hospital/engagingfamilies/strategy3/index.html\">http://www.ahrq.gov/professionals/systems/hospital/engagingfamilies/strategy3/index.html</a><sup class=\"noprint Inline-Template\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&#91;<i><a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Link_rot\" title=\"Wikipedia:Link rot\"><span title=\"&#160;Dead link since November 2016\">permanent dead link</span></a></i>&#93;</span></sup> </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Groves, Patricia S.; Manges, Kirstin (2017-08-24). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dx.doi.org/10.1177/0193945917727237\">\"Understanding Nursing Handoffs: Safety Scholarship in Nursing\"</a>. <i>Western Journal of Nursing Research</i>: 0193945917727237. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1177/0193945917727237\">10.1177/0193945917727237</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number\" title=\"International Standard Serial Number\">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.worldcat.org/issn/0193-9459\">0193-9459</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Western+Journal+of+Nursing+Research&amp;rft.atitle=Understanding+Nursing+Handoffs%3A+Safety+Scholarship+in+Nursing&amp;rft.pages=0193945917727237&amp;rft.date=2017-08-24&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1177%2F0193945917727237&amp;rft.issn=0193-9459&amp;rft.aulast=Groves&amp;rft.aufirst=Patricia+S.&amp;rft.au=Manges%2C+Kirstin&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fdx.doi.org%2F10.1177%2F0193945917727237&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AChange-of-shift+report\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=